'Hello there! It's about time! I've been waiting for service for quite a long while, and this order isn't filling itself, you know.\n\n'Here is my list. Please find these items at once! I haven't got all day.'

Items from the shopping list can be found throughout Bywater during the Farmers Faire. The shopping list is in your inventory.\n\nYou should collect the items on the shopping list...but avoid collecting items that aren't listed!
'Oh, well done, [placeholder]! Filling these orders can be tricky, but I see that you got everything to make this patron happy.\n\nYou are a great help!'
Daisy Sandyman is at her stall at the Farmers Faire in Bywater.\n\nYou should return to Daisy Sandyman at once with the goods you collected.
Collect ingredients on the shopping list
